                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6501" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9522 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分家能过上好日子吗？—生益科技A股第一家分拆生益电子上市</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Can they live a good life apart？—Shengyi technology spin off Shengyi electronics as the first company of A share </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于培友，张美玲，于静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生益电子股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生益科技；生益电子；分拆上市；分拆动因；分拆效果；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shengyi technology, Shengyi electronics, Spin off listing, Spin off motivation, Spin off effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年12月12日，证监会颁布了《上市公司分拆所属子公司境内上市试点若干规定》，该规定开启了我国A股上市公司分拆子公司在境内上市的序幕，第一家“吃螃蟹”的企业是生益科技，其分拆的子公司生益电子于2021年在我国科创板上市，成为我国A股在境内成功分拆上市的首家企业，引起社会各界的广泛关注。本案例以生益科技分拆生益电子上市为主线，描述了行业状况并分别介绍了两家公司的发展历程、概况，对两家公司的关系以及分拆上市的全过程做了详细阐述，最后讲述了生益电子上市后两家公司各自的发展情况。通过本案例引导读者思考分拆上市的动因和效果，对其他拟分拆上市的企业提供启发与借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On December 12, 2019, the CSRC promulgated “several provisions on the pilot domestic listing of subsidiaries of listed companies”, which opened the prelude to the listing of spin off subsidiaries of China&#39;s A-share listed companies. The first enterprise to &quot;eat crabs&quot; is Shengyi technology, and its spin off subsidiary Shengyi Electronics was listed on China&#39;s science and innovation board in 2021, becoming the first enterprise to be successfully spin off and listed in China&#39;s A-share market, attracting extensive attention from all walks of life. Taking the spin off of Shengyi technology and the listing of Shengyi electronics as the main line, this case describes the industry situation, introduces the development process and general situation of the two companies, expounds in detail the relationship between the two companies and the whole process of spin off and listing, and finally describes the respective development of the two companies after the listing of Shengyi electronics. This case guides readers to think about the motivation and effect of spin off listing, and provides inspiration and reference for other enterprises planning to spin off listing.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分拆上市含义与类型；信息不对称理论；融资需求理论；核心化战略理论；价值管理理论；托宾Q理论；超额收益理论；大股东侵占理论；金融市场监管理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
